  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p></p><br><h1>GAMES FROM OUR FRIENDS:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1706297770\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dracula Frames is a slide puzzle game that uses the basis of Dracula's story as motivation.<br><br>Dracula's castle consists of 8 floors. Each floor has a large picture with a magnificent painting representing landmarks of Dracula's life.<br>Your goal is to rebuild each painting through a sliding puzzle and get to the top floor!<br><br>The paintings are cut and shuffled in the jigsaw style, leaving the player to reposition the pieces.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The castle keeps secrets</h2>Discover hidden items. Explore and discover secrets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/e9282227fc49fc3d0c45bdb99fbd586e.poster.avif?t=1706297770\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/e9282227fc49fc3d0c45bdb99fbd586e.webm?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/e9282227fc49fc3d0c45bdb99fbd586e.mp4?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1706297770\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dracula Frames is a slide puzzle game that uses the basis of Dracula's story as motivation.<br><br>Dracula's castle consists of 8 floors. Each floor has a large picture with a magnificent painting representing landmarks of Dracula's life.<br>Your goal is to rebuild each painting through a sliding puzzle and get to the top floor!<br><br>The paintings are cut and shuffled in the jigsaw style, leaving the player to reposition the pieces.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The castle keeps secrets</h2>Discover hidden items. Explore and discover secrets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/e9282227fc49fc3d0c45bdb99fbd586e.poster.avif?t=1706297770\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/e9282227fc49fc3d0c45bdb99fbd586e.webm?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563530/extras/e9282227fc49fc3d0c45bdb99fbd586e.mp4?t=1706297770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
